<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ta">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ஜாதக கோஆர்டினேட் இணைப்பான் - Local DB Edition</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Mukta Malar & Noto Sans Tamil -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mukta+Malar:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+Tamil:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- html2canvas for High Resolution Image Export -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>
    <!-- jsPDF for PDF Generation -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
    
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        tamil: ['Mukta Malar', 'Noto Sans Tamil', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --theme-primary: #991b1b;      /* Red */
            --theme-secondary: #b91c1c;    /* Red Light */
            --theme-bg-light: #fffdec;     /* Traditional yellow-white */
            --theme-bg-tint: #fef2f2;      /* Light Red Tint */
            --theme-border-color: #991b1b;
        }

        .theme-red {
            --theme-primary: #991b1b;
            --theme-secondary: #b91c1c;
            --theme-bg-light: #fffdec;
            --theme-bg-tint: #fef2f2;
            --theme-border-color: #991b1b;
        }

        .theme-blue {
            --theme-primary: #1e3a8a;      /* Navy Blue */
            --theme-secondary: #2563eb;    /* Royal Blue */
            --theme-bg-light: #f8fafc;     /* Clean ice-white */
            --theme-bg-tint: #eff6ff;      /* Light Blue Tint */
            --theme-border-color: #1e3a8a;
        }

        .theme-green {
            --theme-primary: #14532d;      /* Forest Green */
            --theme-secondary: #16a34a;    /* Green Accent */
            --theme-bg-light: #fcfdf5;     /* Eco white */
            --theme-bg-tint: #f0fdf4;      /* Green Tint */
            --theme-border-color: #14532d;
        }

        .theme-purple {
            --theme-primary: #581c87;      /* Deep Purple */
            --theme-secondary: #7e22ce;    /* Violet Accent */
            --theme-bg-light: #fdfafe;     /* Soft Lavender White */
            --theme-bg-tint: #faf5ff;      /* Purple Tint */
            --theme-border-color: #581c87;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Mukta Malar', 'Noto Sans Tamil', sans-serif;
            background-color: #020617;
        }

        /* Applied dynamic theme bindings */
        .theme-text-primary { color: var(--theme-primary) !important; }
        .theme-text-secondary { color: var(--theme-secondary) !important; }
        .theme-border-primary { border-color: var(--theme-primary) !important; }
        .theme-border-secondary { border-color: var(--theme-secondary) !important; }
        .theme-bg-light { background-color: var(--theme-bg-light) !important; }
        .theme-bg-tint { background-color: var(--theme-bg-tint) !important; }

        /* Premium double border style around the entire A4 sheet */
        .premium-sheet-border {
            border: 10px double var(--theme-primary) !important;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Style for interactive editable fields */
        .direct-editable {
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            outline: none;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed transparent;
        }
        .direct-editable:hover {
            border-bottom-color: #f59e0b;
            background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05);
            cursor: text;
        }
        .direct-editable:focus {
            border-bottom-color: #ef4444;
            background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
            border-bottom-style: solid;
        }

        /* Beautiful custom scrollbars */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0f172a;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #334155;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #475569;
        }

        /* South Indian Astrology Grid styling connected to CSS variables */
        .astrology-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(4, 1fr);
            border: 3px solid var(--theme-border-color);
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
            background-color: var(--theme-bg-light);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .astro-cell {
            border: 1.5px solid var(--theme-secondary);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px 4px 8px 4px; /* Added top and bottom padding for safe border spacing */
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1e293b;
            position: relative;
            min-height: 52px; /* Spacing adjusted to give text more breathing room */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .astro-center {
            grid-column: 2 / 4;
            grid-row: 2 / 4;
            background-color: var(--theme-bg-tint);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--theme-primary);
            border: 1.5px solid var(--theme-secondary);
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 0px rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Print sizing container */
        #a4-wrapper {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-out;
            transform-origin: top center;
        }

        /* Active overlay boundary */
        .active-layer {
            border: 2px dashed #f59e0b !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
        }
        .active-layer::after {
            content: "✦ இழுக்கலாம்";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -22px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #f59e0b;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 1px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 50;
        }

        /* Hide element highlights when exporting */
        .exporting .active-layer {
            border: 3px solid var(--theme-primary) !important; /* Retain a solid clean border for photo on export */
            box-shadow: none !important;
        }
        .exporting .active-layer::after {
            display: none !important;
        }
        .exporting .direct-editable {
            border-bottom: none !important;
            background-color: transparent !important;
        }

        /* Form Range Custom Style */
        input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #ef4444;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.1s;
        }
        input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover {
            transform: scale(1.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-100 min-h-screen flex flex-col font-tamil select-none">

    <!-- STICKY TOP HEADER -->
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-slate-900/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800 px-6 py-3 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-2 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-red-900/30">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-yin-yang fa-spin text-xl text-yellow-300"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold tracking-wide text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span>ஜாதக கோஆர்டினேட் இணைப்பான்</span>
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold bg-red-950 text-red-400 border border-red-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Premium Local DB</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Premium Matrimonial Horoscope Multi-Template Builder</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-xs bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md border border-slate-700 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                v5.3 (Overwriting Fixed)
            </span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <button onclick="resetAllSettings()" class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 transition flex items-center gap-1">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i> மீட்க
                </button>
                <button onclick="showInstructions()" class="bg-indigo-950/60 hover:bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-300 text-sm px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-indigo-800 transition flex items-center gap-1">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i> உதவி
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- MAIN DASHBOARD CONTAINER -->
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col lg:flex-row overflow-hidden">
        
        <!-- SIDEBAR CONTROLS (Left Panel) -->
        <aside class="w-full lg:w-[400px] bg-slate-900 border-r border-slate-800 flex flex-col overflow-y-auto shrink-0">
            
            <!-- SECTION 1: PHOTO UPLOAD -->
            <div class="p-5 border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-image text-emerald-400"></i> 1. வரன் புகைப்படம் (File 2)
                </h2>
                
                <div class="relative group border-2 border-dashed border-slate-700 hover:border-emerald-500 rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300 bg-slate-950 text-center cursor-pointer mb-3">
                    <input type="file" id="imageLoader" accept="image/*" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-0 cursor-pointer z-10" />
                    <div id="uploadPlaceholder" class="space-y-2">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up text-slate-400 group-hover:text-emerald-400 text-lg"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 group-hover:text-emerald-300">புகைப்படத்தை தேர்ந்தெடுக்கவும்</span>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">PNG, JPG அல்லது JPEG வடிவங்கள்</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="uploadSuccess" class="hidden space-y-1">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-emerald-400 text-2xl animate-bounce"></i>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-300">புகைப்படம் வெற்றிகரமாக இணைக்கப்பட்டது!</p>
                        <p id="fileName" class="text-xs text-slate-500 truncate max-w-xs mx-auto"></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- NEW BUTTON: Load Sample Portrait SVG Image -->
                <button onclick="loadSamplePhoto()" class="w-full bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-650 text-slate-300 hover:text-white text-xs py-2 px-3 rounded-lg font-bold transition flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-user text-amber-500"></i>
                    <span>மாதிரிப் படம் பயன்படுத்து (Use Sample Photo)</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 2: TEMPLATE SELECTOR -->
            <div class="p-5 border-b border-slate-800">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-violet-400"></i> 2. மாதிரி வடிவமைப்பு (Templates)
                </h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2" id="template-options-container">
                    <!-- Red Theme -->
                    <button onclick="setHoroscopeTheme('red')" id="btn-theme-red" class="theme-option-btn bg-slate-850 hover:bg-slate-800 text-xs py-2.5 px-3 rounded-lg border border-red-500 text-left flex items-center gap-2 transition duration-200">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-red-700 border border-red-400 shrink-0"></span>
                        <div class="leading-tight">
                            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-200">மங்கல சிவப்பு</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">Traditional Crimson</span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                    <!-- Blue Theme -->
                    <button onclick="setHoroscopeTheme('blue')" id="btn-theme-blue" class="theme-option-btn bg-slate-850 hover:bg-slate-800 text-xs py-2.5 px-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 text-left flex items-center gap-2 transition duration-200">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-blue-700 border border-blue-400 shrink-0"></span>
                        <div class="leading-tight">
                            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-200">அரச நீலம்</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">Royal Sapphire</span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                    <!-- Green Theme -->
                    <button onclick="setHoroscopeTheme('green')" id="btn-theme-green" class="theme-option-btn bg-slate-850 hover:bg-slate-800 text-xs py-2.5 px-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 text-left flex items-center gap-2 transition duration-200">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-800 border border-emerald-400 shrink-0"></span>
                        <div class="leading-tight">
                            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-200">பக்தி பசுமை</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">Auspicious Green</span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                    <!-- Purple Theme -->
                    <button onclick="setHoroscopeTheme('purple')" id="btn-theme-purple" class="theme-option-btn bg-slate-850 hover:bg-slate-800 text-xs py-2.5 px-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 text-left flex items-center gap-2 transition duration-200">
                        <span class="w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-full bg-purple-800 border border-purple-400 shrink-0"></span>
                        <div class="leading-tight">
                            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-200">மங்கல ஊதா</span>
                            <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">Divine Purple</span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 3: INNER IMAGE ADJUSTMENT -->
            <div class="p-5 border-b border-slate-800 space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-maximize text-indigo-400"></i> 3. உள்-புகைப்பட சீரமைப்பு (Aspect Fit)
                </h2>

                <!-- Zoom -->
                <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                        <span class="text-slate-300">அளவை கூட்டு (Zoom)</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-indigo-400 font-bold" id="val-zoom">100%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6">100%</span>
                        <input type="range" id="slider-zoom" min="100" max="300" value="100" class="flex-1 h-1.5 bg-slate-850 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6 text-right">300%</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pan X -->
                <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                        <span class="text-slate-300">இடப்பக்க நகர்வு (Pan X)</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-indigo-400 font-bold" id="val-pan-x">0px</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6">-200px</span>
                        <input type="range" id="slider-pan-x" min="-150" max="200" value="0" class="flex-1 h-1.5 bg-slate-850 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6 text-right">200px</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pan Y -->
                <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="flex justify-between text-xs">
                        <span class="text-slate-300">மேலெழுந்த நகர்வு (Pan Y)</span>
                        <span class="font-mono text-indigo-400 font-bold" id="val-pan-y">0px</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6">-150px</span>
                        <input type="range" id="slider-pan-y" min="-150" max="200" value="0" class="flex-1 h-1.5 bg-slate-850 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 w-6 text-right">200px</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SECTION 4: LOCAL DATABASE & BACKUP -->
            <div class="p-5 border-b border-slate-800 space-y-4 bg-slate-900/40">
                <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-database text-amber-400"></i> 4. உள்ளூர் சேமிப்பகம் (Local Storage)
                </h2>
                
                <!-- Input for profile name with overwrite support -->
                <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <label class="text-xs text-slate-400 block">கோப்பு பெயர் (File / Profile Name):</label>
                        <!-- Reset active profile ID button to allow Save As New -->
                        <button id="btn-new-profile" onclick="startNewProfile()" class="text-[10px] text-amber-500 hover:text-amber-400 font-bold hidden flex items-center gap-1">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-plus"></i> புதிய கோப்பு உருவாக்க
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <input type="text" id="db-profile-name" placeholder="உதா: கார்த்திக் ஜாதகம்" class="flex-1 bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-500">
                        <button onclick="saveCurrentProfile()" class="bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg font-bold transition shrink-0 flex items-center gap-1">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i> சேமிக்க
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- File import/export actions -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-1">
                    <button onclick="exportProfileAsJSON()" class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 text-[10px] py-2 px-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 transition flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-export text-indigo-400"></i> கணினியில் சேமி
                    </button>
                    <label class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 text-[10px] py-2 px-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 transition flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer text-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-import text-teal-400"></i> கோப்பைத் திற
                        <input type="file" id="json-file-input" accept=".json" class="hidden" onchange="importProfileFromJSON(event)">
                    </label>
                </div>

                <!-- Saved list -->
                <div class="space-y-1.5">
                    <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 block font-bold">சேமிக்கப்பட்ட ஜாதகங்கள் (Browser DB):</span>
                    <div id="saved-profiles-list" class="max-h-40 overflow-y-auto space-y-1.5 pr-1 text-xs">
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-[11px] italic text-center py-2">சேமிக்கப்பட்ட விவரங்கள் எதுவும் இல்லை.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- EXPORT ACTIONS PANEL -->
            <div class="p-5 mt-auto bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-800 space-y-3">
                <button onclick="exportAsImage()" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-600 to-amber-600 hover:from-rose-500 hover:to-amber-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-rose-950/50 transition duration-150 transform active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-file-image text-lg"></i>
                    <span>File 3 - ஆக மாற்றுக (JPEG)</span>
                </button>
                <button onclick="exportAsPDF()" class="w-full bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-200 font-semibold py-2.5 px-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 transition duration-150 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-file-pdf text-red-500"></i>
                    <span>PDF ஆக பதிவிறக்குக</span>
                </button>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 text-center">அச்சிட உகந்த 300 DPI துல்லியத் தரத்தில் பதிவிறக்கம் செய்யப்படும்.</p>
            </div>

        </aside>

        <!-- LIVE INTERACTIVE WORKSPACE (Right Panel) -->
        <main class="flex-1 bg-slate-950 overflow-auto p-4 md:p-8 flex flex-col items-center relative">
            
            <!-- CANVAS VIEWPORT CONTROL HEADER -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-[794px] flex items-center justify-between mb-4 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400">
                    <span class="inline-block w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                    <span>உள்ளார்ந்த மாதிரிக் காட்சி (A4 Sheet Preview with Borders)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
